decks.notes: This deck is focused on aggressive gameplay, aiming to quickly reduce the opponent's life total. It utilizes aggressive creatures such as Kari Zev, Skyship Raider and Monastery Swiftspear to deal damage early on. The deck also includes burn spells like Play with Fire and Stoke the Flames to remove threats or finish off the opponent. Atarka's Command and Reckless Bushwhacker provide additional burst damage and pumping power to the team. The deck makes use of land cards like Den of the Bugbear and Sokenzan, Crucible of Defiance to enhance its aggression and maintain a fast pace.
